Young-eun also made the same request of me.

808
00:52:26,371 --> 00:52:27,422
At the time,

809
00:52:27,505 --> 00:52:29,674
I just thought it was
a momentary feeling...

810
00:52:31,843 --> 00:52:33,144
but it seems that wasn't the case.

811
00:52:34,378 --> 00:52:35,713
I beg you...

812
00:52:36,914 --> 00:52:38,215
for my mom.

813
00:52:41,885 --> 00:52:42,886
Talk...

814
00:52:43,887 --> 00:52:46,223
to that doctor...

815
00:52:47,391 --> 00:52:48,359
and make it so my mom...

816
00:52:50,661 --> 00:52:52,162
can pass away peacefully.

817
00:52:52,930 --> 00:52:53,664
Do it.

818
00:52:56,299 --> 00:52:57,734
Because of my selfishness,

819
00:52:59,169 --> 00:53:03,006
my mom has been suffering and only
receiving ineffective treatments.

820
00:53:04,174 --> 00:53:06,109
Now she doesn't know anything anymore...

821
00:53:08,178 --> 00:53:10,947
and she'll forget all her memories.

822
00:53:14,017 --> 00:53:17,454
I can't let her die suffering.

823
00:53:18,889 --> 00:53:19,789
Young-eun.

824
00:53:20,757 --> 00:53:21,825
I beg you.

825
00:53:23,627 --> 00:53:24,833
Help my mom.

826
00:53:25,999 --> 00:53:27,264
Please, help her.

827
00:53:42,646 --> 00:53:44,660
Until now, for whatever reason...

828
00:53:45,915 --> 00:53:49,286
I thought that giving up one's life
willingly shouldn't be allowed...

829
00:53:51,655 --> 00:53:53,023
but now I'm not so sure anymore.

830
00:53:54,924 --> 00:53:55,717
I just...

831
00:53:56,960 --> 00:53:58,228
wish that Auntie...

832
00:53:59,596 --> 00:54:01,064
could feel more comfortable.

833
00:54:11,741 --> 00:54:13,410
I'll be back after work.

834
00:54:14,344 --> 00:54:16,246
Let's talk face to face later.

835
00:54:55,550 --> 00:54:57,386
It seems like she's going
through a very difficult time.

836
00:55:00,122 --> 00:55:01,957
That old woman is really unfortunate.

837
00:55:02,691 --> 00:55:05,827
It seems she has dementia.
Doesn't she know her own daughter died?

838
00:55:08,764 --> 00:55:10,332
- Who are you?
- Me?

839
00:55:12,100 --> 00:55:13,368
I'm my brother's sister.

840
00:55:15,270 --> 00:55:16,338
Gu Gwang-chul.

841
00:55:17,806 --> 00:55:19,241
You know him well, right?

842
00:55:22,577 --> 00:55:25,304
Work with me again, okay?

843
00:55:26,948 --> 00:55:29,067
I want to see your skills before that,
so I'll make you a proposal.

844
00:55:29,150 --> 00:55:31,403
No, I don't accept any proposals.

845
00:55:31,486 --> 00:55:32,420
You know...

846
00:55:34,522 --> 00:55:36,557
Kill my husband, please.

847
00:55:43,765 --> 00:55:44,783
Is your husband very sick?

848
00:55:44,867 --> 00:55:47,219
No, he's too healthy. That's the problem.

849
00:55:47,302 --> 00:55:49,837
He has so much energy that he
goes around doing useless things.

850
00:56:03,050 --> 00:56:05,119
<i>Didn't you think Lee Yun-hee
and Song-i looked alike?</i>

851
00:56:05,986 --> 00:56:07,638
Kill me.

852
00:56:07,721 --> 00:56:08,839
<i>The mother got sick.</i>

853
00:56:08,922 --> 00:56:10,107
My mom...

854
00:56:10,190 --> 00:56:11,424
has only suffered.

855
00:56:12,192 --> 00:56:13,810
<i>The daughter only dedicates
herself to taking care of her.</i>

856
00:56:13,893 --> 00:56:15,362
She's only received pain.

857
00:56:16,563 --> 00:56:18,932
<i>Please, don't ignore my mom.</i>

858
00:56:19,966 --> 00:56:22,152
Please, help her.

859
00:56:22,235 --> 00:56:23,036
<i>I...</i>

860
00:56:23,570 --> 00:56:25,038
Can't I say...

861
00:56:26,306 --> 00:56:27,374
how I want...

862
00:56:27,874 --> 00:56:30,861
my end to be?

863
00:56:30,944 --> 00:56:32,545
<i>At least let her be
comfortable at the end...</i>

864
00:56:33,280 --> 00:56:34,598
<i>Shouldn't she go in peace?</i>

865
00:56:34,681 --> 00:56:35,899
<i>I just wish Auntie...</i>

866
00:56:36,340 --> 00:56:37,784
would feel more comfortable.

867
00:56:38,385 --> 00:56:39,586
At the end...

868
00:56:40,401 --> 00:56:42,022
if everything goes well...

869
00:56:42,856 --> 00:56:44,591
so I can go in peace...

870
00:56:45,325 --> 00:56:47,190
<i>that kind of medicine...</i>

871
00:56:47,273 --> 00:56:49,195
<i>isn't that what's most needed?</i>

872
00:56:51,998 --> 00:56:54,017
<i>Let me go with my daughter.</i>

873
00:56:54,100 --> 00:56:56,386
<i>Why have I lived until now?</i>

874
00:56:56,469 --> 00:56:59,789
<i>I've lived to see her face one more time.</i>

875
00:56:59,872 --> 00:57:01,124
<i>I can't live.</i>

876
00:57:01,207 --> 00:57:02,110
<i>Please, let me go.</i>

877
00:57:02,194 --> 00:57:03,041
<i>I just...</i>

878
00:57:07,246 --> 00:57:08,247
<i>Euthanasia.</i>

879
00:57:09,716 --> 00:57:11,651
<i>There are definitely patients who need it.</i>

880
00:57:39,245 --> 00:57:41,130
So, killing a healthy person...?

881
00:57:41,213 --> 00:57:42,982
Are you asking me
to kill you with euthanasia?

882
00:57:43,683 --> 00:57:44,717
Can't you?

883
00:57:47,520 --> 00:57:49,688
Have you never killed a healthy person?

884
00:58:09,873 --> 00:58:14,078
TREATMENT ROOM

885
00:58:26,824 --> 00:58:27,858
Dr. Woo So-jeong.

886
00:58:42,906 --> 00:58:43,974
Help me.

